Yep, and the source of one of the world&#39;s greatest mondegreens. A 
mondegreen is a misheard song lyric.  Do a web search for the term to find 
out its history.

But the line in Purple Haze &quot;Excuse me while I kiss the sky&quot; was often 
heard by people to be &quot;Excuse me while I kiss this guy.&quot;
:-)

